main event: A sighting of a small man-made object was reported by a civilian in Parsippany, New Jersey on November 12, 1967.
interesting points: The observer noted that the object looked like two paper plates with a domed shape,The object produced a humming noise during the sighting,Animals in the vicinity were reported to be barking,The sighting lasted for approximately 20 seconds,The photograph of the object was later identified as a hoax.
sighted object: a small object resembling two paper plates
witness description: The observer and a friend saw the object along with the observer's parents, who later denied seeing it.
